nodeTraining.title: Exposure Visit of MSOCB Team to KSOCA from 27th November 2023 to 1st December 2023

body.processed: As a new CB to be established, the team from the Meghalaya State Organic Certification Body (MSOCB) visited Karnataka State Organic Certification Agency (KSOCA) for an exposure visit. The purpose of the visit is to understand the certification process, the challenges and the strategy involved therein.
